import React, { useState } from 'react';
import {
  Box, Typography, TextField, Grid, Paper, Button,
} from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const ApplicationFormBPT = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  const [formData, setFormData] = useState({
    adNo: '',
    adDate: '',
    applicationNo: '',
    courseName: '',
    courseCode: '',
    dateOfEntry: '',
    lastDate: '',
    department: '',
    name: '',
    fatherName: '',
    dob: '',
    age: '',
    birthPlace: '',
    status: '',
    nationality: '',
    maritalStatus: '',
    gender: '',
    differentlyAbled: '',
    idMark1: '',
    idMark2: '',
    universityArea: '',
    inService: '',
    aadhar: '',
    fatherEmail: '',
    fatherAge: '',
    fatherOccupation: '',
    motherName: '',
    motherAge: '',
    motherOccupation: '',
    monthlyIncome: '',
  });

  const handleChange = (field) => (event) => {
    setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, [field]: event.target.value }));
  };

  const handleSubmit = () => {
    navigate('/report', { state: formData });
  };

  return (
    <Box sx={{ pt: 4, px: 6, pb: 7 }}>
      <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom align="center">
        APPLICATION FORM - Bachelor of Physiotherapy - 2025
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Advertisement Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Advertisement Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Ad. No." fullWidth value={formData.adNo} onChange={handleChange('adNo')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Ad. Date" fullWidth value={formData.adDate} onChange={handleChange('adDate')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Application No." fullWidth value={formData.applicationNo} onChange={handleChange('applicationNo')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Course Name" fullWidth value={formData.courseName} onChange={handleChange('courseName')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Course Code" fullWidth value={formData.courseCode} onChange={handleChange('courseCode')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Date of Entry" fullWidth value={formData.dateOfEntry} onChange={handleChange('dateOfEntry')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Last Date of Application" fullWidth value={formData.lastDate} onChange={handleChange('lastDate')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Department" fullWidth value={formData.department} onChange={handleChange('department')} /></Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Applicant's Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Applicant's Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Name" fullWidth value={formData.name} onChange={handleChange('name')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Father's Name" fullWidth value={formData.fatherName} onChange={handleChange('fatherName')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Date of Birth" fullWidth value={formData.dob} onChange={handleChange('dob')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Age (on last date)" fullWidth value={formData.age} onChange={handleChange('age')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Place of Birth" fullWidth value={formData.birthPlace} onChange={handleChange('birthPlace')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Social Status" fullWidth value={formData.status} onChange={handleChange('status')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Nationality" fullWidth value={formData.nationality} onChange={handleChange('nationality')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Marital Status" fullWidth value={formData.maritalStatus} onChange={handleChange('maritalStatus')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Gender" fullWidth value={formData.gender} onChange={handleChange('gender')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Differently Abled" fullWidth value={formData.differentlyAbled} onChange={handleChange('differentlyAbled')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Identification Mark 1" fullWidth value={formData.idMark1} onChange={handleChange('idMark1')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Identification Mark 2" fullWidth value={formData.idMark2} onChange={handleChange('idMark2')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="University Area" fullWidth value={formData.universityArea} onChange={handleChange('universityArea')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="In-service (Govt.)" fullWidth value={formData.inService} onChange={handleChange('inService')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Aadhar" fullWidth value={formData.aadhar} onChange={handleChange('aadhar')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}><TextField label="Father's Email" fullWidth value={formData.fatherEmail} onChange={handleChange('fatherEmail')} /></Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Parent/Spouse Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Parents' Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Father's Name" fullWidth value={formData.fatherName} onChange={handleChange('fatherName')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Age" fullWidth value={formData.fatherAge} onChange={handleChange('fatherAge')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Occupation" fullWidth value={formData.fatherOccupation} onChange={handleChange('fatherOccupation')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Mother's Name" fullWidth value={formData.motherName} onChange={handleChange('motherName')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Age" fullWidth value={formData.motherAge} onChange={handleChange('motherAge')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Occupation" fullWidth value={formData.motherOccupation} onChange={handleChange('motherOccupation')} /></Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}><TextField label="Monthly Income" fullWidth value={formData.monthlyIncome} onChange={handleChange('monthlyIncome')} /></Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Submit Button */}
        <Grid item xs={12} textAlign="center">
          <Button variant="contained" color="primary" onClick={handleSubmit}>
            Submit
          </Button>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default ApplicationFormBPT;
